Author: basicomplex
Text: Eh, if they're just skinny cause of high metabolism than that shits gonna catch up to them in the long run. I'm more envious of people who know how to have self control and actually work on the body they have. There is no way someone is binging on food and looking thin without having some ED. And if they're not binging, well, than I don't care cause I want my damn cookies.

Author: skitof
Text: I hate hearing this crap from non disordered people. I'm sorry about that.
